{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_RemovePod}}
'''A_RemovePod'''<br>
(no parameters)<br>

Decreases by one the <code>special1</code> field of the calling actor's master.

A {{Class|PodGenerator}} uses this field to count how many children it has currently spawned with [[A_MakePod]]. This function is restricted to classes inheriting from {{Class|Pod}} because the same field might be used by other special actors or restricted codepointers for different purposes.

[[category:Decorate Heretic functions]] [[Category:Decorate Restricted functions]]{{DEFAULTSORT:RemovePod}}
